DNS Entries
A RECORDS

$> dig <worker1 name>.<domain name> +short

$> dig <worker0 name>.<cluster name>.<domain name>  +short

$> dig etcd-0.<cluster name>.<domain name> +short

$> dig etcd-1.<cluster name>.<domain name>  +short

$> dig etcd-2.<cluster name>.<domain name>  +short


CNAME RECORDS
$> dig api.<cluster name>.<domain name> +short

$> dig api-int.<cluster name>.<domain name> +short

$> dig apps.<cluster name>.<domain name> +short

$> dig test.apps.<cluster name>.<domain name> +short [ tests the "*" record ]


SRV RECORDS
$> dig _etcd-server-ssl._tcp.<cluster name>.<domain name> srv


REVERSE RECORDS (there are TWO per IP, I can change that if needed)
